{"tid":2172004,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[隆重宣佈] 吊打唔撚係台語，係支那用語。","createTime":"2020-08-24T10:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T10:17:55.000Z","uid":36861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"157420de0e41f0e8469a4ca818067c477b1a383e","tid":2172004,"uid":36861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:17:55.000Z","msg":"成班支那細蚊仔係大埔某M記係度一邊開住王者定傳說，一邊講&rdquo;你被我吊打你&rdquo;(支那語) 。身邊個香港同學仔用廣東話講&rdquo;我先唔會俾你屌打&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n直頭係耳濡目染。<br />\n<br />\n我本身對支那細蚊仔無咩歧視，但唔該你地啲港豬家長放學就即刻捉個仔返屋企，唔好俾佢哋痴埋啲支那同學到啦，教壞曬。<br />\n<br />\n 施捨個良好嘅教育環境比支那細蚊仔唔緊要，但至少你哋都要感恩圖報，學下本地語言。<br />\n<br />\n支那語同狗吠無咩分別。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}